  <brief_title>Study in Myeloma Patients Newly Diagnosed Treated as an Induction With Velcade-Dex or Velcade (Bortezomib) Thalidomide Dexamethasone (VTD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3 Study of Velcade (Bortezomib) Dexamethasone (VD) Versus Velcade (Bortezomib) Thalidomide Dexamethasone (VTD) as an Induction Treatment Prior to Autologous Stem Cell Transplantation in Patients With Newly Diagnosed Multiple Myeloma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
